text: Kyungon, United States National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency is a village in Wuntho Township, Katha District, in the Sagaing Region of northern-central Burma (Myanmar). ==Notes== ==External links== *"Kyungon Map — Satellite Images of Kyungon" Maplandia World Gazetteer Category:Populated places in Katha District
